Package: leakr
Type: Package
Title: Data Leakage Detection Tools for Machine Learning
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Cheryl Isabella Lim
Maintainer: Cheryl Isabella Lim <cheryl.academic@gmail.com>
Description: Provides utilities to detect common data leakage patterns including train/test contamination, temporal leakage, and data duplication,
  enhancing model reliability and reproducibility in machine learning workflows. Generates diagnostic reports and visual summaries to support data validation.
Imports: ggplot2, arrow, data.table, digest, htmltools, openxlsx, readxl, stringr, workflows, jsonlite
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0), caret, mlr3, tidymodels, knitr, rmarkdown
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
LazyData: false
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
